node.text:
Announcing the public beta release of MechPic (on IOS and Android) an app designed for marking up storing and sharing technical images and photos 

With this app you can 

- Add tags to your photos so you can find them later
- Add text and arrows to the image
- Add text above and below the image
- Add a title 
- Have your name easily added to the image so you always get credit for what you shared
- Share and download great training images from throughout the trades
- Get access to my entire training illustration library 

Please download, try it out and let me know any issues or comments 

Also... It is free 

Thanks
